      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== STATS BAR ====== -->
  <div class="hp-stats">
    <div class="hp-stats__grid">
      <div class="hp-stat"><div class="hp-stat__number" data-count="100">0</div><div class="hp-stat__label">全力投入</div></div>
      <div class="hp-stat"><div class="hp-stat__number" data-count="3">0</div><div class="hp-stat__label">項服務</div></div>
      <div class="hp-stat"><div class="hp-stat__number" data-count="10">0</div><div class="hp-stat__label">週計劃</div></div>
      <div class="hp-stat"><div class="hp-stat__number" data-count="2">0</div><div class="hp-stat__label">個國家</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <!-- ====== FAQ ====== -->
  <section class="hp-section hp-faq" id="faq">
    <div class="hp-container">
      <div class="hp-header-center">
        <div class="hp-label">問題</div>
        <h2 class="hp-heading">家長常問的問題</h2>
        <p class="hp-subtitle">坦白的回答。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-faq__list">
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>如果孩子想家怎麼辦？</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>我們每週跟進。與三位導師的群組聊天。我們把每位球員當作自己的孩子。你的孩子在加拿大絕不孤單。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>如果球隊不合適怎麼辦？</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>我們在安置前就進行評估。我們了解教練。我們做過很多次了。如果有問題，我們會及早處理。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>你們保證安置嗎？</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>不。我們保證努力。我們不做出無法兌現的承諾。但我們安置球員是因為我們做好工作。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>我怎麼和孩子保持聯繫？</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>我們的每週更新。教練溝通。WhatsApp 群組。你會知道每一步的情況。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-faq-item">
          <button class="hp-faq-item__question"><h3>費用是多少？</h3><div class="hp-faq-item__icon"></div></button>
          <div class="hp-faq-item__answer"><p>這取決於服務。<a href="#contact">聯繫我們</a>聊聊孩子的需求和適合的方案。</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== CTA ====== -->
  <section class="hp-cta" id="contact">
